            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258624</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla 在香港圆方举办「遇见未来 Meet The Future」限定体验活动，今次更是 Tesla 首次在香港展示旗下先进机械人产品—Tesla Optimus。同场亦展出了极具未来感的 Cybertruck 及全新 Quicksilver 闪电银色车色版本 Model 3 和 Model Y。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Optimus 机械人（又名 Tesla Bot）是一款设计灵感来自人类形态的人形机械人，专为替代人类进行重复、枯燥或危险工作而研发。Optimus 采用与 Tesla 电动车相同人工智能 AI 技术，能够安全高效地在复杂环境中自主导航及操作人类工具、搬运货物，以及在工厂里工作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Optimus</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手部设计可操作人类工具</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/3-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/3-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/3-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可搬运货物</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258706" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/4-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/4-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/4-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲具有多个活动关节</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_2-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_2-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_2-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲采用与 Tesla 电动车相同人工智能 AI 技术</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258700" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_3-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_3-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meetthefuture_3-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>Cybertruck 是一辆外观设计具有未来感，同时兼顾实用性和跑车性能的电动卡车，拥有卓越的耐用性及全地形驾驶能力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258707" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/5-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/5-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/5-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Tesla 同场展示了全新 Quicksilver 闪电银色 Model 3 和 Model Y，这款颜色会随光线及观看角度变化呈现不同视觉效果，令车身流线设计更加突出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 闪电银色 Model Y</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258709" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 闪电银色 Model Y</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/9-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/9-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 闪电银色 Model 3</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quicksilver 闪电银色 Model 3</p><p>Tesla 同时推出针对 Model 3 和 Model Y 后轮驱动版本的免息分期贷款计划，名额有限，先到先得。有兴趣试驾的朋友可透过 Tesla 官方网站 <a href="https://bit.ly/TeslaMeetTheFuture">https://bit.ly/TeslaMeetTheFuture</a> 预约，或致电 3975-0254 查询详情。</p><h2>「遇见未来 Meet The Future」限定体验活动</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 18.3691%;"><strong>日期：</strong></td><td style="width: 81.6309%;">2024 年 8 月 24 日至 9 月 1 日</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 18.3691%;"><strong>时间：</strong></td><td style="width: 81.6309%;">11:00-20:00</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 18.3691%;"><strong>地点：</strong></td><td style="width: 81.6309%;">圆方金区 1 楼</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/23/tesla-drive-anywhere-package-us/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 美国推出新服务计划，超级充电站 FSD 自动驾驶 3 年任用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/eu-update-chinese-ev-tariffs/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">欧盟调低中国电动车额外关税，三大中国车企减幅极少 Tesla 受惠最大</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/13/donald-trump-elon-musk-talk-on-x/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">特朗普马斯克网络对谈听众过百万　赞扬 Tesla 电动车「不可思议」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/tesla-optimus-robot-in-element/life-tech/auto/">香港抢先睇 Tesla Optimus 机械人　同场展出 Cybertruck、Model 3 + Model Y 新闪电银色</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
